FBIS3-47598 "dreas010_c_94016" FBIS-EAS-94-010 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Jan 1994 North Korea WPK Delegation Leaves for Italy, France SK1301103894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1020 GMT 13 Jan 94 SK1301103894 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, January 13 (KCNA) -- A delegation of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] led by Pak Kyong-son, vice-director of a department of the C.C. [Central Committee], WPK, left here today to participate in the national congress of the Italian Party for Communist Refoundation and the 28th congress of the French Communist Party. It was seen off at the airport by Chi Chae-yong, vice-director of a department of the C.C., WPK.
